      <div class="font-body text-[17.6px] leading-[1.5] text-[#757575] space-y-4">
        <p>Are you considering launching a sportswear business in Vietnam but finding it difficult to identify reliable and cost-effective manufacturers? As a newcomer to the industry, it’s essential to work with production partners that not only offer high-quality products but also align with your budget and brand vision.</p>
        <p>Understanding these concerns, we introduce you to four of the top sportswear manufacturers in Vietnam trusted names that combine craftsmanship, modern technology, and international standards. Alongside this, we’ll explore how Vietnam’s garment manufacturing sector is emerging as a global powerhouse.</p>
        <h4 class="font-heading text-[24px] font-medium leading-[1.2] text-[#1D2F40] text-center">Why Vietnam is the Ideal Destination for Sportswear Manufacturing</h4>
        <p>Vietnam is currently one of the world’s top five garment and textile exporters, known for its skilled labor, competitive costs, efficient logistics infrastructure, and business-friendly environment. The country continues to attract global investors and fashion startups thanks to complete value chains, industrial zones, cost-effective labor, and experienced OEM/ODM factories.</p>
        <h4 class="font-heading text-[24px] font-medium leading-[1.2] text-[#1D2F40]">Top 4 Sportswear Manufacturers in Vietnam</h4>
        <p>When it comes to sportswear manufacturing, ICM Factory Direct stands out as one of the most innovative and reliable partners in Vietnam, serving high-profile clients like Hard Rock Cafe, JW Marriott, Mercedes-Benz, Ironman Triathlon, and Super League.</p>
        <p>ICM is consistently ranked among the top sportswear manufacturers in Vietnam, with strong emphasis on personalization, digital transformation, and sustainable production.</p>
        <p><strong>ICM's cutting-edge technologies include:</strong></p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-4">
          <li><strong>Virtual Fit & Custom Fit using Computer Vision AI</strong> — Athletes can submit front and side photos to generate precise body measurements, allowing for virtual try-ons and a customized fit.</li>
          <li><strong>Sublimation Printing for High-Impact Branding</strong> — Vibrant, fade-resistant prints are perfectly aligned to body shape using AI-enhanced design positioning.</li>
          <li><strong>Laser Cutting for Precision and Efficiency</strong> — Automated laser cutting ensures fabric optimization, perfect pattern accuracy, and reduced waste.</li>
          <li><strong>Smart Textiles Integration</strong> — ICM uses performance-enhancing fabrics embedded with sensors for temperature control, moisture management, and real-time performance tracking.</li>
          <li><strong>Seamless Construction Technology</strong> — Delivers garments with minimal stitching for enhanced comfort, durability, and athletic mobility.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>With a firm commitment to innovation, premium materials, and exceptional service, ICM Factory Direct is leading the future of personalized sportswear manufacturing in Vietnam and beyond.</p>

        <h4 class="font-heading text-[24px] font-medium leading-[1.2] text-[#1D2F40] mt-8">2. Dugarco</h4>
        <p>A longstanding name in Vietnam's apparel industry, Dugarco operates with a strong focus on quality control, timely delivery, and sustainability. With headquarters in Hanoi and multiple factories nationwide, the company employs skilled technicians and modern equipment across several production lines.</p>
        <p>Dugarco specializes in a wide range of products including:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-4">
          <li>Sportswear (jackets, uniforms, shirts, trousers)</li>
          <li>Corporate and performance wear</li>
          <li>Knitwear and casualwear</li>
        </ul>
        <p>With a global client base, Dugarco combines tradition with modern practices to deliver consistent excellence.</p>

        <h4 class="font-heading text-[24px] font-medium leading-[1.2] text-[#1D2F40] mt-8">3. OnTrack</h4>
        <p>If your brand is focused on combat sportswear or premium athletic gear, OnTrack is a highly specialized manufacturer worth considering. They are experts in crafting high-performance wear for:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-4">
          <li>MMA, Boxing, and Brazilian Jiu-Jitsu (BJJ)</li>
          <li>Training apparel, protective gear, and uniforms</li>
        </ul>
        <p>With a strong emphasis on durability, fit, and technical design, OnTrack utilizes advanced materials and production technologies to meet the rigorous standards of combat sports athletes.</p>

        <h4 class="font-heading text-[24px] font-medium leading-[1.2] text-[#1D2F40] mt-8">4. An Thang Garment Co., Ltd</h4>
        <p>An Thang is a full-service OEM/ODM garment factory that handles everything from sample development to packaging and delivery. They specialize in:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-4">
          <li>Sportswear and activewear</li>
          <li>Private label apparel</li>
          <li>Custom branding and embroidery</li>
        </ul>
        <p>With modern sewing facilities and a flexible production model, An Thang supports CM, CMP, OEM, ODM, and FOB orders of various sizes. Their dedication to quality, turnaround time, and customer satisfaction makes them a valuable partner for startups and established brands alike.</p>

        <h4 class="font-heading text-[24px] font-medium leading-[1.2] text-[#1D2F40] text-center mt-8">Supporting Infrastructure & Global Readiness</h4>
        <p>What further sets Vietnam apart from other manufacturing countries is its robust infrastructure:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-4">
          <li>Proximity to shipping ports and well-established logistics in industrial zones like Binh Duong, Long An, and Bac Ninh</li>
          <li>Favorable government policies that support FDI, tech adoption, and sustainable practices</li>
          <li>Access to local suppliers for fabrics, trims, and accessories, reducing lead times and shipping costs</li>
        </ul>
        <p>This ecosystem ensures that Vietnamese manufacturers like ICM Factory Direct can offer speed-to-market capabilities, ideal for fast-growing DTC brands or sportswear startups scaling globally.</p>

        <h4 class="font-heading text-[24px] font-medium leading-[1.2] text-[#1D2F40] text-center mt-8">Conclusion: Scale Your Sportswear Business with Vietnam's Best</h4>
        <p>Vietnam's sportswear manufacturing sector is fast becoming the go-to destination for brands seeking a balance of cost, quality, and innovation. By partnering with top-tier manufacturers like ICM Factory Direct, Dugarco, OnTrack, and An Thang, you gain:</p>
